OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering PC
OL,4,CSharon Beshenivsky
OL,6,FA man who evaded justice for almost 19
OL,7,Fyears has been found guilty of the
OL,8,F2005 murder of West Yorkshire Police
OL,9,Fofficer Sharon Beshenivsky.
OL,11,FPiran Ditta Khan, 75, was the
OL,12,Fringleader of an armed robbery at a
OL,13,Ftravel agents in Bradford during which
OL,14,FPC Beshenivsky was fatally shot.
OL,16,FHe was the last of seven men to face
OL,17,Ftrial, having been extradited from
OL,18,FPakistan last year.
