OL,4,CSharon Beshenivsky
OL,6,FIt took the jury at Leeds Crown Court
OL,7,Falmost four days to reach a majority
OL,8,Fverdict.
OL,10,FKhan, who admitted robbery and was
OL,11,Falso found guilty of firearms
OL,12,Foffences, will be sentenced at a later
OL,13,Fdate.
OL,15,FPC Beshenivsky, a 38-year-old mother-
OL,16,Fof-three, was shot dead after
OL,17,Fresponding to reports of a raid at
OL,18,FUniversal Express travel agents on
OL,19,FMorley Street, Bradford, on 18
OL,20,FNovember 2005. Her colleague PC Teresa
OL,21,FMilburn was also shot but survived.
