OL,6,FSpeaking outside court Det Supt Marc
OL,7,FBowes said: "While we welcome today's
OL,8,Fconviction our thoughts are firmly
OL,9,Fwith PC Sharon Beshenivsky, Teresa
OL,10,FMilburn and their family and friends.
OL,12,F"Sharon and Teresa went to work that
OL,13,Fday, back in November 2005, fully
OL,14,Fexpecting to come home to their family
OL,15,Fand friends. Due to the horrific
OL,16,Factions of those individuals that have
OL,17,Fnow been convicted that wasn't the
OL,18,Fcase."
