OL,6,FHe added: "I would like to acknowledge
OL,7,Fthe respect and dignity that Sharon's
OL,8,Ffamily have shown over the last 18
OL,9,Fyears and I hope that today's
OL,10,Fconviction goes some way in enabling
OL,11,Fthem to move on with their lives.
OL,12,FSharon Beshenivsky lost her life in
OL,13,Fthe most horrific of circumstances in
OL,14,Fthe line of duty and she will always
OL,15,Fbe remembered."
